<h3>Mailing List</h3>
<div class="vevent">

Subscribe to the ChicagoLUG mailing list, or <a href="http://groups.google.com
/group/chicagolinux-discuss">view the archives</a>. Our mailing list is hosted
by Google Groups.

<form action="http://groups.google.com/group/chicagolinux-discuss/boxsubscribe">
<p><label for="google_email">Email: </label><input id="google_email" type=
text name=email /><input type=submit name="sub" value="Subscribe" /></p>
</form>
</div>

<h3>Social Media</h3>
<div class="vevent">

Announcements about meetings and events will be posted to this site and to our
social media outlets.

- [Google Plus](https://plus.google.com/110920643277848720575?prsrc=3)
- [Twitter](https://twitter.com/chicagolug)
- [Identi.ca](https://identi.ca/chicagolug)
- [Meetup.com](http://www.meetup.com/Windy-City-Linux-Users-Group/)

</div>

<h3>Internet Relay Chat (IRC)</h3>
<div class="vevent">

The ChicagoLUG IRC channel is #chicagolug on irc.freenode.net.

</div>

